<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>Favorite Foods</title>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="bootstrap-4.1.3-dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="fontawesome-free-5.5.0-web/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-dark bg-dark">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="index.html">Ethan Boadu</a>
            <ul class="nav nav-pills">
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link " href="index.html"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Activities</a></li>

                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="home.html"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Home Page</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="life.html"><i class="fas fa-user"></i> My Life</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="movies.html"><i class="fas fa-film"></i> Favorite Movies</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link active" href="foods.html"><i class="fas fa-utensils"></i> Favorite Foods</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container mt-4 text-center">
        <div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
            Welcome to my Favorite Foods page! Here are some of the dishes I love the most.
        </div>
        <h1 class="mb-4">My Favorite Foods</h1>
        <p>These foods remind me of my home in Ghana, where my family and I enjoyed traditional dishes and seafood.</p>
        
        <div class="row">
            <!-- Fried Rice Card -->
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <%= image_tag "Fried Rice.jpg", class: "card-img-top", alt: "Fried Rice" %>
                <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Fried Rice</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">I love Fried Rice because it's flavorful and reminds me of family gatherings.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-utensils"></i> Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <%= image_tag "Jollof.jpg", class: "card-img-top", alt: "Jollof" %>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Jollof Rice</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Jollof Rice is a staple in Ghanaian cuisine, and it's always a must-have at celebrations!</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-utensils"></i> Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

           
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <%= image_tag "seafood.jpg", class: "card-img-top", alt: "seafood" %>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Seafood</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Seafood brings back memories of trips to the coast with my family.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-utensils"></i> Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

           
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <%= image_tag "waakye.jpg", class: "card-img-top", alt: "Waakye" %>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Waakye</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Waakye is a delicious combination of rice and beans, often enjoyed with spicy sauces.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-utensils"></i> Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-4">
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="index.html">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Index
        </a>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer text-center mt-4">
        <div class="container">
            <span class="text-muted">Thanks for learning about my favorite foods! 🍛</span>
        </div>
    </footer>

 
    <script src="bootstrap-4.1.3-dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    
    <script src="fontawesome-free-5.5.0-web/js/all.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

